<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Coxinhas da Mamãe</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        header {
            background-color: #FF6F61;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 2.5em;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            border-radius: 10px;
        }
        .coxinhas {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: space-around;
        }
        .coxinha {
            background-color: #FFF3E0;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin: 10px;
            padding: 15px;
            text-align: center;
            flex: 1 1 300px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .coxinha img {
            max-width: 100%;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }
        .coxinha h3 {
            margin-top: 10px;
            font-size: 1.5em;
        }
        .coxinha p {
            font-size: 1.2em;
        }
        .cta {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .cta a {
            background-color: #FF6F61;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }
        .cta a:hover {
            background-color: #E65C50;
        }
        footer {
            background-color: #333;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
    <h1>Coxinhas da Mamãe</h1>
    <p>Deliciosas coxinhas artesanais feitas com amor!</p>
</header>

<div class="container">
    <h2>Sabores e Valores</h2>
    <div class="coxinhas">
        <div class="coxinha">
            <img src="coxinha-frango.jpg" alt="Coxinha de Frango">
            <h3>Coxinha de Frango</h3>
            <p>R$ 5,00</p>
        </div>
        <div class="coxinha">
            <img src="coxinha-carne.jpg" alt="Coxinha de Carne">
            <h3>Coxinha de Carne</h3>
            <p>R$ 6,00</p>
        </div>
        <div class="coxinha">
            <img src="coxinha-vegana.jpg" alt="Coxinha Vegana">
            <h3>Coxinha Vegana</h3>
            <p>R$ 7,00</p>
        </div>
    </div>o

    <div class="cta">
        <a href="https://wa.me/seunumerodetelefone">Peça Agora pelo WhatsApp</a>
    </div>
</div>

<footer>
    <p>&copy; 2024 Coxinhas da Mamãe. Todos os direitos reservados.</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
